name: Jumping jacks
details: Jumping jacks improve cardiovascular fitness, boost heart health, and burn calories. They strengthen muscles in the legs, core, and shoulders.

name: Running
details: Running boost cardiovascular health, enhance coordination, and burn calories. They tone leg and core muscles, improve endurance, and support weight loss.

name: Cycling
details: Cycling enhance cardiovascular fitness, strengthen leg muscles, and improve coordination. They boost metabolism, aiding in calorie burning and weight management.

name: Swimming
details: Swimming improve cardiovascular endurance and strengthen muscles, particularly the legs, core, and upper body.

name: Dynamic stretches
details: Dynamic stretches improve flexibility and range of motion, preparing muscles for activity. They enhance blood flow, reduce injury risk, and improve performance.

name: Yoga
details: Yoga enhances flexibility, strength, and balance. It reduces stress, improves mental clarity, and boosts mood through mindfulness and relaxation

name: Meditation
details: Meditation reduces stress, lowers blood pressure, and enhances emotional health. It improves focus, memory, and self-awareness.
